<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink333">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi yāvatum</l>
<l>vallā kollō tāmē yavaṇa</l>
<l>kalluṭai naṉṉāṭṭup puḷḷiṉap peruntō</l>
<l>ṭiyāan tuṇaipuṇarn tuṟaitum</l>
<l>yāṅkup pirintuṟaiti yeṉṉā tavvē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Alas! May you live long, my friend!</l>
<l>Listen!  The huge flocks of bird kind in the good land full of rocks, </l>
<l>that belong to that place – aren’t they capable even a little? </l>
<l>None of them asks: “We live together with [our] companions! </l>
<l>How do you live in separation?” </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
